<item>
            <title>[OAK-2880] NPE in SegmentWriter.writeMap</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-2880</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Under some rare conditions which are not entirely clear yet &lt;tt&gt;SegmentWriter.writeMap&lt;/tt&gt; results in a &lt;tt&gt;NPE&lt;/tt&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;java.lang.NullPointerException
	at com.google.common.base.Preconditions.checkNotNull(Preconditions.java:192)
	at org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.plugins.segment.SegmentWriter.writeRecordId(SegmentWriter.java:366)
	at org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.plugins.segment.SegmentWriter.writeMapLeaf(SegmentWriter.java:417)
	at org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.plugins.segment.SegmentWriter.writeMapBucket(SegmentWriter.java:475)
	at org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.plugins.segment.SegmentWriter.writeMapBucket(SegmentWriter.java:511)
	at org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.plugins.segment.SegmentWriter.writeMap(SegmentWriter.java:711)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This happens when the &lt;tt&gt;base&lt;/tt&gt; passed to &lt;tt&gt;writeMap(MapRecord base, Map&amp;lt;String, RecordId&amp;gt; changes)&lt;/tt&gt; is not null but doesn&apos;t contain some of the keys &lt;b&gt;removed&lt;/b&gt; through the updates provided in the passed &lt;tt&gt;changes&lt;/tt&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
